&lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://news.bis.gov.uk/content/detail.aspx?NewsAreaId=2&amp;amp;ReleaseID=423725&amp;amp;SubjectId=2"&gt;Press Notice - Government seeks views on dismissal process&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Th&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.bis.gov.uk//policies/employment-matters/employment-law-review"&gt;e Employment Law Review&lt;/a&gt;
